data.title: Dive into anything
data.text:
What radio stations here are best for the following kinds of music?

Top 40

Pop

Hip Hop

Dance

Alternative Rock

90s

00s

80s

I have 18 slots to fill in my car and I can't seem to find stations I like in this town because it seems like most stations don't come in. Apart from just tuning through every station and waiting to see what kind of music it is, I thought asking here might be helpful.

I don't mind if the station is your run-of-the-mill "plays the same songs over and over" kinda thing - because most of the time I use my Youtube Music account. But not always and I hate hearing static when I turn my car on.
